/// each spawn. `seen_content_pane` defers this past the boot race with the
/// layout's `--slot main` viewer; `respawn_in_flight` debounces it until
/// the new pane lands in a later manifest. A lingering held/exited pane is
/// swapped in place so a fresh viewer does not stack on top of a dead one.
